  <li>Which Suburbs are most costly  and least costly ?</li>
  <li>How the prices change with the
    <ul>
      <li>number of room(s)</li>
      <li>number of bedroom(s)</li>
      <li>distance from CBD</li>
      <li>type of the house</li>
      <li>building area</li>
      <li>number of bathroom(s)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

